high_descs: Turn to the right and face the right side of the desk.
Pick up the pencil on the desk.
Step to the right and face the night stand on the left side of the bed.
Place the pencil in the drawer of the night stand.
Step forward to face the night stand.
Pick up the pencil on top of the night stand.
Step back to face the drawer of the night stand.
Place the pencil in the drawer with the other pencil.
anns.task_desc: To move two pencils in the drawer of the night stand to the left of the bed.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the right side of the desk.
Take the pencil to the right of the book on the desk.
Turn around, go forward a step, turn right, go forward, stop half way to the bed, turn left.
Put the pencil in the top drawer of the night stand.
Turn right, go forward to the bed, turn left, go forward to the night stand.
Take the pencil from the night stand.
Move backwards and to the left from the night stand. Face the night stand.
Put the pencil in the top drawer of the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Put two pencils in a night stand drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the wooden desk.
Pick up the yellow pencil to the right of the book on the desk.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk towards the bed, turn left to face the nightstand next to the bed.
Open the upper nightstand drawer and put the pencil in it, then close the drawer.
Turn right and walk towards the bed, then turn left and walk up to the nightstand.
Pick up the pencil off of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the nightstand.
Open the upper nightstand drawer and put the pencil inside.
anns.task_desc: Move two pencils into a drawer.
